EDI Document 852 - Product Activity Data
Function:
The EDI 852 Product Activity Data document is used to provide trading partners with detailed information on sales and inventory levels for specific products.

Example:

ISA*00*          *00*          *ZZ*SENDERID      *ZZ*RECEIVERID    *YYMMDD*HHMM*U*00501*000000001*0*P*>~
GS*PD*SENDERID*RECEIVERID*YYMMDD*HHMM*1*X*005010~
ST*852*0001~
BDS*00*ORIGINAL CONTROL NUMBER*ORIGINAL DATE*ORIGINAL TIME*TRANSACTION TYPE*ORIGINAL REFERENCE NUMBER~
DTM*002*20230701~
N1*SU*SUPPLIER NAME*92*SUPPLIERID~
LIN*1*PRODUCT CODE*UPC*PRODUCT DESCRIPTION~
UIT*EA~
PO4*1*100*EA~
DTM*010*20230701~
SE*10*0001~
GE*1*1~
IEA*1*000000001~

Purpose in Lizgate Enterprise:
In Lizgate Enterprise, the EDI 852 document enhances inventory management by providing accurate product activity data, enabling effective demand forecasting and inventory replenishment strategies.